Class Summary
PrimeEncodeProver Class responsible for proving that a PrimeEncode predicate holds.

Package com.ibm.zrl.idmx.showproof.pe Description

This package contains the code to implement Idemix proving protocol for prime encoded attributes. The main classes are PrimeEncodeProver and PrimeEncodeVerifier which play the corresponding roles in the proving protocol (these classes are used by the Prover and Verifier).

See Also:
com.ibm.zrl.idmx.showproof, com.ibm.zrl.idmx.showproof.predicates, com.ibm.zrl.idmx.showproof.sval
